  <li><a href="https://github.com/Microsoft/language-server-protocol">Language Server Protocol Specification</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://www.eclipse.org/community/eclipse_newsletter/2017/may/article1.php">Language Server Protocol - Eclipse Newsletter May 2017</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://github.com/Microsoft/vscode-languageserver-node">VS Code‚Äôs Implementation of the Language Server Protocol</a></li>
  <li><a href="http://langserver.org/">Langserver.org - Information about other language servers and clients, e.g., Atom, Sublime, Vim, etc</a></li>
